{
  "key_path": "RoleRoomAdminDescription",
  "content": "Room admins can create and manage the assigned rooms, invite new users and assign roles below their level. All admins have access to the {{sectionName}} section.<br/> <1>In {{agentSection}}</1>: can create and manage {{agentSection}}, including their knowledge base and access settings.",
