  "comment": {
    "text": "This is a description of the Room Admin role, displayed in tooltips or information sections. It explains the permissions of a Room Admin, including managing rooms, inviting users, and accessing the `sectionName` (e.g., \"Documents\") and `agentSection` (e.g., \"AI Assistant\") sections. The `1` tag bolds specific text.",
